 |archive-date = 2013-05-15
 |dead-url     = yes
}}</ref>接替任期届满的原首席大法官拉姆·普拉萨德·什雷斯塔。<ref>{{cite news
 |title        = Regmi named new Chief Justice
 |url          = http://www.ekantipur.com/2011/04/11/capital/regmi-named-new-chief-justice/332357.html
 |date         = 11 April 2011
